{"article_id":"LNYpRp5Sd3YLhWlC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Back in October 2016 , Sen. Dianne Feinstein","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"called then-FBI Director James Comey ' s decision","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"to look into new Hillary Clinton emails just days before the election","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"\" appalling. \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Her comment reflected the general sentiment among Democrats at the time .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"But in May 2017 , President Donald Trump fired Comey","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"because the FBI wouldn ' t end an investigation into a former top Trump aide ' s Russia ties .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Democrats , almost in unison , openly warned","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"that dismissing Comey meant Trump may have tried to obstruct justice .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"after reports surfaced","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that Trump had called Comey a \" nut job , \"","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Feinstein herself defended the former FBI director ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that \" Comey is no way , shape , or form a nut job . \"","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"As Comey now sits down for high-profile interview after high-profile interview","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"- like he did on ABC on April 15 -","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to promote his new book ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"expect the good feelings from Democrats and the media alike to keep coming .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Comey ' s new memoir , A Higher Loyalty , is due to come out on Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"In it , highly critical of Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"and the tome will assuredly inspire more Comey fandom on television , radio , and print .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"It may lead to even more arguments , like Damon Linker ' s in the Week last June ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"\" that the former FBI director is a bona fide American hero . \"","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"But painting Comey that way misses a lot .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"He led the FBI","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"when the bureau possibly mishandled its investigation into Clinton ' s use of a private email server","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"when she was secretary of state ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"perhaps costing Hillary Clinton the election .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"He was also the FBI director","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"when he oversaw increased surveillance of Muslim communities and a culture of suspicion against Muslims","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and used suspect methods","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"to stop terrorists .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Put together ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"as the Washington Post ' s Margaret Sullivan noted on March 31 ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Comey is undeserving of the veneration and softball questions","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"he will surely field in the coming days in response to his much-hyped new book .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"That , in part , is because he did a successful job","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"at cultivating his holier-than-thou persona ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"says Matthew Miller , a top Justice Department spokesperson in the Obama administration .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"\" He wanted to position himself as the hero ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"\"","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Miller told me ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"\" the man of integrity","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"who was going to tell the American people how it is","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"- the last virgin in town . \"","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"The problem , though , is that the media fell for it .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"At around 11 am on July 5 , 2016 , then-FBI Director Comey gave a surprise televised address","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"- thrusting him into the national spotlight .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"\" This will be an unusual statement in at least a couple ways , \"","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"he admitted from the FBI ' s lectern .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"\" I am going to include more detail about our process","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"than I ordinarily would ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"because I think","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"the American people deserve those details in a case of intense public interest . \"","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"The \" case \" in question was the FBI ' s probe into Clinton ' s use of a personal email server","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"to conduct State Department business .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Investigators wanted to know","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"if Clinton had handled classified information on an insecure network ,","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"which could make it easier for foreign adversaries to steal top secrets .","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"But Comey recommended no criminal charges to the Justice Department ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"instead reprimanding her as \" extremely careless \"","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"after finding 110 emails","depth":16},{"id":64,"text":"containing classified information","depth":16},{"id":65,"text":"among the 30,000 reviewed messages .","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"The following day , then-Attorney General Loretta Lynch accepted Comey ' s choice","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"not to charge Clinton .","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"( Lynch had just days before that decision met with Bill Clinton on an Arizona tarmac ,","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"leading to calls for her recusal from the case . )","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"Comey , in effect , closed the case .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"According to an April 2017 New York Times report about Comey ' s actions during the election ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"he chose this approach for a few reasons .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"First , to let those people within the FBI","depth":16},{"id":74,"text":"who were upset with Clinton ' s conduct","depth":16},{"id":75,"text":"know","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"that Comey heard and understood their concerns .","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"But second , and most importantly , he aimed to shield the bureau from GOP-led attacks","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"that the FBI took it easy on Clinton .","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"Those attacks came anyway .","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"\" This announcement defies explanation .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"No one should be above the law , \"","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan tweeted after Comey ' s remarks .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" It appears damage is being done to the rule of law . \"","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"But the more controversial moment came three months later .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"As part of a probe into former Rep. Anthony Weiner '","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"s ( D-NY )","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"sexually explicit conversations with a minor , the FBI found some of Clinton ' s emails on his laptop .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"That was no coincidence :","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Huma Abedin , Weiner ' s wife and a close Clinton aide at the State Department , backed up thousands of emails on her husband ' s computer .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"Some agents believed","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"Clinton had hid emails from them ,","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"adding to suspicions","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"that the messages on Weiner ' s laptop might just be the missing emails .","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"And then on October 28 , Comey informed Congress of what happened in a letter :","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"\" In connection with an unrelated case , the FBI has learned of the existence of emails","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that appear to be pertinent to the investigation . \"","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"It was the \" October surprise \"","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"many feared","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"- the reopening of an investigation into Clinton just 11 days before the election .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"According to polling expert Nate Silver ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Comey changed the vote ' s outcome","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"by making the probe ' s restart public :","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"Clinton ' s standing in the polls fell sharply .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"She ' d led Trump by 5.9 percentage points in FiveThirtyEight ' s popular vote projection at 12:01 a.m. on Oct. 28 .","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"A week later","depth":16},{"id":106,"text":"- after polls had time","depth":17},{"id":107,"text":"to fully reflect the letter -","depth":17},{"id":108,"text":"her lead had declined to 2.9 percentage points .","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"That is to say ,","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"there was a shift of about 3 percentage points against Clinton . ...","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"In the average swing state , Clinton ' s lead declined from 4.5 percentage points at the start of Oct. 28 to just 1.7 percentage points on Nov. 4 .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"If the polls were off even slightly ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Trump could be headed to the White House .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"Silver ' s chart dramatically shows the effect","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"the letter seemed to have on the election .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"To be clear ,","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"the problem here is not that Comey ' s actions helped Trump beat Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"It ' s that his actions likely had an impact on the election .","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"The FBI is chiefly an apolitical institution ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"carrying out investigations","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"regardless of the political moment .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"So for Comey to act the way","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"he did","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"- especially at the time","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"that he did -","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"made it seem like he overstepped his mandate .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"\" The way","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"he handled the Clinton investigation","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"was seriously flawed and arguably a firing offense , \"","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"Miller , the former top DOJ spokesperson , told me .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Comey wrestles with his decision in the new book .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"\" It is entirely possible that ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"because I was making decisions in an environment","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"where Hillary Clinton was sure to be the next president ,","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"my concern","depth":16},{"id":136,"text":"about making her an illegitimate president","depth":17},{"id":137,"text":"by concealing the restarted investigation","depth":17},{"id":138,"text":"bore greater weight","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"than it would have","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"if the election appeared closer","depth":16},{"id":141,"text":"or if Donald Trump were ahead in all polls , \"","depth":16},{"id":142,"text":"he writes .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"\" But I don ' t know . \"","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"Let ' s be clear about what he ' s saying :","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Comey admits","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Clinton ' s lead in late October may have influenced his decision","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"to reopen the probe","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"and let the public know about it .","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"That means he possibly allowed politics to dictate his actions","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"- which looks really bad for the FBI director .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"But Miller thinks","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"Comey ' s view of himself also played a part .","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"\" He ' s a man of integrity ,","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"but he very much believes","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"he ' s a man of integrity","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"and often thinks","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"he ' s the only honest man in the room , \"","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"he told me .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"\" At some point , that self-confidence crosses a line into self-righteousness . \"","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"Comey ' s imprint on the election results is bad enough .","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"The Justice Department ' s inspector general will look into , and soon adjudicate on , how the FBI handled the Clinton probe .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"But you also just need to look at Comey ' s time running the FBI","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"to know","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"he ' s not Mr . Perfect .","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"Comey led the FBI for four years -","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"and has faced a fair amount of criticism for his time there .","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"For one , Muslims","depth":14},{"id":168,"text":"working at the FBI","depth":14},{"id":169,"text":"felt","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"their fellow agents put them under a microscope .","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"Most notably , these employees felt","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"the FBI would overly scrutinize them","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"because of their heritage .","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"Former FBI employee Said \" Sam \" Barodi ,","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"according to the Guardian ,","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"detailed how some white FBI officials were openly Islamophobic ,","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"said","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"Islam was to blame for acts of terrorism ,","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"and that some colleagues didn ' t abide by the Constitution .","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"\" I would not advise anyone to work for the FBI under these circumstances .","depth":14},{"id":181,"text":"Fuck , stay away .","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"It is not worth it .","depth":16},{"id":183,"text":"It is cancer , \"","depth":16},{"id":184,"text":"Barodi told the Guardian .","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"\" Muslim employees in federal law enforcement , \"","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"he continued ,","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"\" are the target . \"","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"But that ' s not all .","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"Comey also expanded the use of sting operations","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"to catch would-be terrorists","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"before they struck ,","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"and some of the practices were suspect .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"Last May , the Intercept reported","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"that agents \" busted \" a mentally ill homeless man","depth":14},{"id":195,"text":"for claiming","depth":15},{"id":196,"text":"he had connections to ISIS .","depth":15},{"id":197,"text":"In a similar case , an informant also gave a homeless man $ 40","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"so he could buy the weapons","depth":16},{"id":199,"text":"- machetes , knives -","depth":16},{"id":200,"text":"he said","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"he needed","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"to carry out the attack .","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"Meanwhile , those stings didn ' t stop actual terrorists .","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"As the Intercept notes ,","depth":16},{"id":205,"text":"the FBI looked at least twice at the man","depth":17},{"id":206,"text":"who eventually killed nearly 50 people","depth":18},{"id":207,"text":"and wounded another 50 at an Orlando nightclub in June 2016 .","depth":18},{"id":208,"text":"The FBI , apparently , didn ' t consider the man a threat during its investigations .","depth":15},{"id":209,"text":"And","depth":16},{"id":210,"text":"when the FBI charged the creator of the child porn dark website Playpen last year ,","depth":17},{"id":211,"text":"the bureau didn ' t shut down the service .","depth":17},{"id":212,"text":"That reversed the practice","depth":16},{"id":213,"text":"Robert Mueller","depth":18},{"id":214,"text":"- Comey ' s predecessor and now the special counsel","depth":19},{"id":215,"text":"looking into possible Trump-Russia ties -","depth":19},{"id":216,"text":"started .","depth":17},{"id":217,"text":"Still , the FBI made hundreds of arrests in the US and around the world throughout the case ,","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"while also identifying or rescuing nearly 300 sexually abused children .","depth":14},{"id":219,"text":"In short , Comey wasn ' t exactly an exemplary leader","depth":5},{"id":220,"text":"when he was in charge of the FBI .","depth":5},{"id":221,"text":"Yet the \" Comey is a hero \" myth persists","depth":5},{"id":222,"text":"- though perhaps that says more about us than him .","depth":5},{"id":223,"text":"Why we see Comey as a hero","depth":4},{"id":224,"text":"- but shouldn ' t","depth":4},{"id":225,"text":"The impulse","depth":9},{"id":226,"text":"to lionize Comey","depth":9},{"id":227,"text":"comes from the fact","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"that he stood up to Trump .","depth":7},{"id":229,"text":"When Trump demanded Comey pledge his loyalty to him ,","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"the FBI director declined .","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"After Trump fired Comey last May ,","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"Comey revealed","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"that he kept contemporaneous notes about his interactions with the president","depth":11},{"id":234,"text":"and made parts of them public .","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"He also testified under oath during a high-profile Senate hearing last June ,","depth":9},{"id":236,"text":"in which he shockingly called the president a liar .","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"Put together ,","depth":7},{"id":238,"text":"this makes Comey stands out as a seemingly noble figure in the middle of the whole Trump-Russia mess ,","depth":8},{"id":239,"text":"where Mueller ' s probe has already found","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"that high-level Trump campaign officials committed crimes .","depth":9},{"id":241,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":242,"text":"if you take a second look ,","depth":8},{"id":243,"text":"that ' s a pretty low bar .","depth":8},{"id":244,"text":"Comey may seem like the closest thing","depth":7},{"id":245,"text":"this drama has to a hero","depth":7},{"id":246,"text":"- except for maybe Mueller himself -","depth":6},{"id":247,"text":"but that doesn ' t mean the media should forget his complicated past ,","depth":6},{"id":248,"text":"and treat him like one .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":497,"left":264,"right":496,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":254,"right":263,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":253,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":250,"right":252,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":250,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":251,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":255,"right":262,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":256,"right":261,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":261,"left":259,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":258,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":10,"right":257,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":257,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":496,"left":470,"right":495,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":470,"left":466,"right":469,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":466,"left":295,"right":465,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":267,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":266,"right":19,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":266,"left":265,"right":18,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":280,"right":293,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":272,"right":279,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":269,"right":271,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":268,"right":22,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":270,"right":25,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":275,"right":278,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":26,"right":274,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":273,"right":29,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":30,"right":277,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":31,"right":276,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":292,"right":47,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":283,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":34,"right":282,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":35,"right":281,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":281,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":285,"right":290,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":284,"right":40,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":287,"right":289,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":287,"left":41,"right":286,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":44,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":465,"left":365,"right":464,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":365,"left":362,"right":364,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":362,"left":330,"right":361,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":330,"left":326,"right":329,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":326,"left":302,"right":325,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":296,"right":301,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":48,"right":49,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":297,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":298,"right":299,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":325,"left":311,"right":324,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":311,"left":303,"right":310,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":303,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":305,"right":309,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":58,"right":304,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":304,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":61,"right":308,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":62,"right":307,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS